I was wondering if anyone has ever completed it from 1st to 10th without sufficient faction? (using sneak).<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=92579">Milvas</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> Threepwood <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ubiggwin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Biggwin</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/17/02 8:02:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10745.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Coldain ring quest</span><hr size=1> Can Complete up to 9 at least being Max KoS to Thurg... buddy was on the 10th ring when he retired and is Ally Kael. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uflatin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Flatin</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/17/02 8:09:56 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10745.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Coldain ring quest</span><hr size=1> I've done 1-7 sneaking. <br>
<br>
Few things to know:<br>
Ring 2 - did it with myself and KOS cleric. Make sure you kill giants that guarding fort in EW. After Boradain got through that part, he will head to jail, rest on the way. This is your chance to kill 2 orcs in jail area. After boradain is done with jail area, make sure that 2 orcs who guard rygorr entrance are dead. If Boradain aggroed on me or cleric, I could atone just fine.<br>
<br>
Ring 4 - Kinda tricky. Tain didnt respond to me while sneaking too well, so some druid helped me by spawning giants. Bring some help, you need someone to kite 4 giants around. Turnin went smoothly, didnt aggro the dorf.<br>
<br>
Ring 6 - As soon as you hand in the ring to Korrigan, HIDE IMMIDIATELY. Never happened to me, but alot of folks aggroed icefang this way.<br>
<br>
Ring 7 - I suggest cleric or druid help. Do the turn in, follow Corbin around, when giants spawn, aggro him and train towards the water. Bring him close to coldain camp he's going to and rootpark him. Single pull coldain missionary from the hut, kill. Missionary is a cleric and will CH till he's OOM, stuns would help. As soon as missionary is dead, camp yourself and whoever rooted Corbin to clear aggro. Memwipe wont work, Corbin will turn around, go to jail, go back towards coldain camp and spawn giants again. Once again, coldain missionary HAS TO BE DEAD or you lose your rings.<br>
<br>
Ring 8 - I got dubios by the time I did that. But if you are KOS, you have to be VERY PRECISE on your timing. Make sure you kill chief really fast. Wizzy or some other damage dealer helps. As soon as Garadain calls charge, make sure that no dorf is behind you and hand in. This is a hard part, alot of people lost rings on this turnin<br>
<br>
Ring 9 - Dont think it's doable while KOS, not sure on this<br>
<br>
Ring 10 - Impossible to do while KOS. People who assist you with war can be KOS, but not the person who's running the war.<br>
<br>
